  "title": "7506 - First Article Inspector (3 Months Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>First Article Inspector</strong><br /><strong>Contract: 3-Months </strong><em><strong>(May have extensions based on project needs)</strong></em><br /><br />Working Hours: 8.30am - 5pm<br />Working Days: Monday - Friday<br />Salary: $ 2300 - $ 2400<br />Working Location: Pioneer MRT<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform First Article Inspection and prepare First Article Inspection Reports (FAIR).</li><li>Submit FAIR at customer portal for approval.</li><li>Review internal inspection reports.</li><li>Review supplier FAIR and communicate with supplier for first article issues.</li><li>Perform administrative tasks such as document preparation and collection.</li><li>Perform other related duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in mechanical or electrical engineering.</li><li>Training provided.</li><li>Ability to read and comprehend mechanical drawings, technical specifications and product certifications.</li><li>Good working knowledge of inspection technique.</li><li>Hands-on knowledge on basic measuring tools such as caliper.</li><li>Basic Microsoft Office skills.</li><li>Previous experience in FAIR preparation is preferred.</li></ul><p><br /><br /><strong>Chin See Min Reg No. : R22107450</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No. : 14C7279</strong></p>",
